author: rjollos
msg: Removed unused "milestone owner" code from the milestone view template.

The "milestone owner" code can be re-added if //owner// is added ot the milestone model. The code currently renders //Assigned to ${milestone.name}//, which needs to be changed to //Assigned to ${milestone.owner}//. Refs #93.
